== Cingkrik == '''Cingkrik''' '''''n''''' ''(Betawi)''
A style of silat from Jakarta. The legend said the system came from Rawabelong, created by Ki Maing. One of the characteristic of the system is a movement called ''jejingkrikan'' where the practitioner hope in one leg.
