==Dominance==
{{blockwrap|ta=left|
A strategy <math> s_i </math> is '''strictly dominant''' iff:<br> <math> \forall s_j \neq s_i \in \mathbb{\mathcal{S}}:\quad U(s_i,s_{-i})>U(s_j,s_{-i})</math><br>
A strategy <math> s_i </math> is '''weakly dominant''' iff:<br> <math> \forall s_j \neq s_i \in \mathbb{\mathcal{S}}:\quad U(s_i,s_{-i})\geq U(s_j,s_{-i})</math>
}}

