====Seamless Textures====
Mostly textures have to be tile able. Therefore no edges should be visible if the image is repeated.<br/>
A great, very useful helper is the Photshop filter->sonstige Filter-> Verschiebungseffekt.<br/>
It is very useful to create edge free patterns.
