File:Blender-appli2biped-pose-example3.png|Different Movements
File:Blender-appli2biped-pose-example2.png
File:Blender-appli2biped-pose-example1.png
File:Blender-appli2biped-pose-example.png
File:Blender3D SimpleWalkCycle.gif
</gallery>
