==PhotoElectric== Light of certain Energy shines on some material generates Electricity . This effect is called PhotoElectric : hf = hfo + <math>\frac{1}{2}m v^2</math> : f > fo for v > 0
''Photon Light of Quantum Energy E = hf has the capability to generate Electricity when shines on Light conducting materials '' consists # Visible Light # UVF Light # X Ray # Gamma Ray
